"make" to compile files
"make example1" to run example1 script
"make example2" to run example2 script
"make clean" to remove .o files and tilda files
"make clear" to remove .o files, tilda files, and main.exe

suggested uses:
"./main.exe <filename>" (see below)
"make example1 clean"
"make example2 clean"
"make example1 clear"
"make example2 clear"

main.exe expects the filename of the script as an argument